{"id": 2491, "genre": 1001, "title": "你心中的“中年危机”都有哪些表现？", "description": "对你来说，“中年”和“中年危机”的区别是啥？哪些迹象可以算得上“中年危机”？（图片来自：iStock © scotellaro）", "record_count": 4242, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180731100453SbyWq7IkgFNiVHex.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-31T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 296192, "content": "没有说走就走的自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412644}, {"id": 296448, "content": "当自己对未来放弃希望，才算得上中年危机，否则中年不过是人生新的开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419143}, {"id": 296193, "content": "生活艰难，等待我的只有死亡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781352}, {"id": 296194, "content": "开始有白头发了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716159}, {"id": 296195, "content": "孩子在长大，我在老去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206809}, {"id": 296198, "content": "百度百科中，中年是指“45~59岁”\n还有很多不同的搜索结果，似乎没有明确划分", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396855}, {"id": 296199, "content": "当然是形象和健康，被爱的人嫌弃，例如秃头，怨妇，和社会脱轨，不爱学习等，对生活充满了无望", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423048}, {"id": 296711, "content": "生完孩子回去工作被鸠占鹊巢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425629}, {"id": 296200, "content": "忌讳越来越多，路越走越看不到希望", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423053}, {"id": 296456, "content": "还没有一个人，两间房，三顿饭，四代同堂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424219}, {"id": 296201, "content": "知道了不惑之年是什么意思。感觉时间不够用，家庭、事业与爱好之间很难平衡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305466}, {"id": 296202, "content": "担心十几年积累的资产随时可能大幅度贬值。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358156}, {"id": 296203, "content": "觉得人生好像就是这样和那样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423075}, {"id": 296460, "content": "知道成为女王的梦想没有了……?哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405892}, {"id": 296205, "content": "还在守着自己的一亩三分地", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383647}, {"id": 296717, "content": "还有好多事没起尝试，还有好多地方没留下我的脚印。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425658}, {"id": 297229, "content": "父母变老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427203}, {"id": 296206, "content": "还在守着自己的一亩三分地", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383647}, {"id": 296208, "content": "内心失去希望", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740193}, {"id": 296209, "content": "开始跟不上时代的脚步\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399537}, {"id": 296210, "content": "错过了就真的过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243870}, {"id": 296211, "content": "男，年龄越大，越找不到男朋友，。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403383}, {"id": 296212, "content": "认命了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423130}, {"id": 295958, "content": "胖出来的肉 饿几顿也减不下去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 241, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306695}, {"id": 296214, "content": "这大概是20几岁人的警示指南吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773145}, {"id": 296470, "content": "穷坏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568501}, {"id": 295959, "content": "00后开始上大学了", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119373}, {"id": 296215, "content": "会越来越越重视养生同时又不自觉地做着不养生的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280576}, {"id": 296727, "content": "越来越懒 越来越觉得生活没激情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425709}, {"id": 295960, "content": "三十而立", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770804}, {"id": 296216, "content": "干啥都累", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423140}, {"id": 296472, "content": "掉头发…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424280}, {"id": 295961, "content": "རང་གི་ནུས་པ་དང་ཧམ་པ་དོ་མི་མཉམ་པ། ཕུག་བསམ་ངེས་གཏན་མེད་པ།", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395095}, {"id": 296217, "content": "发际线越来越高，头发越来越稀疏", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280576}, {"id": 295962, "content": "渐渐发现自己不适合熬夜了，而且开始蜜汁清淡的菜单还自我感觉良好", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422150}, {"id": 295963, "content": "担心35岁失业", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144988}, {"id": 296475, "content": "脱发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403135}, {"id": 295964, "content": "每天都化妆，男同事却问你是不是从来不化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286302}, {"id": 296220, "content": "路上小朋友叫阿姨，已经成为表哥表姐的孩子的姑姑和叔叔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366478}, {"id": 295965, "content": "以前熬夜第二天依旧活蹦乱跳，现在一熬夜就焉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 222, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414988}, {"id": 296477, "content": "依旧默默无闻！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424298}, {"id": 295966, "content": "什么都不怕，虽然很平凡，不富裕，像我们这种没信仰，没梦想的，估计就是娶不到老婆这一危机感了吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406302}, {"id": 295967, "content": "知道人生某些可能性再也没有了", "image": null, "praise_count": 604, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1167629}, {"id": 295968, "content": "00后的孩子都开始上学了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407114}, {"id": 296224, "content": "孩子们的作业做起来越来越吃力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423175}, {"id": 295969, "content": "腰开始酸了", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414850}, {"id": 296225, "content": "怕时间过得太快，哎！失去的往往比得到的还要多。到了中年剩下的也就寥寥无几了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422040}, {"id": 295970, "content": "如果还没有找到另一半，那么我就是我家的最后一个了，我死了我的财产要给谁呢_(:з」∠)_", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371402}, {"id": 295972, "content": "越来越不在意自己的形象，素质越来越低下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359104}, {"id": 296740, "content": "耕耘是要得，但心气却没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384746}]}